ZH: 他栽了一株花。
EN: He planted a flower.

ZH: 这个冬天我打算栽点儿植物。
EN: I’m planning to grow some plants this winter.

ZH: 他经营的农场栽了很多果树。
EN: He planted a lot of fruit trees in his farm.

ZH: 我帮他挑选了一些适合栽种的花草。
EN: I helped him choose some suitable flowers and plants for planting.

ZH: 这种树要找一个阳光充足的地方栽种。
EN: This tree needs to be planted in a place with plenty of sunlight.

ZH: 把这些树苗栽到这块地里吧。
EN: Plant these saplings in this area.

ZH: 他不善于栽培植物。
EN: He is not good at cultivating plants.

ZH: 这里的土地不适合栽种大面积的庄稼。
EN: The land here is not suitable for planting crops on a large scale.

ZH: 她栽种的花儿已经长得很茂盛了。
EN: The flowers she planted have grown lush.

ZH: 我们栽了一排树来修建行道树。
EN: We planted a row of trees to build a shade.

ZH: 风太大了，我担心树会栽倒。
EN: The wind is too strong, I'm afraid the tree will fall over.

ZH: 他被迫将栽种的庄稼全部拔掉。
EN: He was forced to uproot all the crops he planted.

ZH: 这片土地可栽种各种蔬菜。
EN: Various vegetables can be grown in this piece of land.

ZH: 他栽了许多盆栽在家里。
EN: He planted many potted plants at home.

ZH: 这个花坛栽了许多漂亮的花。
EN: Many beautiful flowers were planted in this flower bed.

ZH: 他们一起栽了一个菜园。
EN: They planted a vegetable garden together.

ZH: 这颗苹果树已经栽了五六年了。
EN: This apple tree has been planted for five or six years.

ZH: 这块地不适合栽种庄稼。
EN: This piece of land is not suitable for planting crops.

ZH: 我们栽植的庄稼长得非常茂盛。
EN: The crops we planted grew very lush.

ZH: 他们栽种了一些耐旱的植物。
EN: They planted some drought-resistant plants.

ZH: 我去买点儿花球栽在花盆里。
EN: I'm going to buy some flower bulbs to plant in pots.
